{"tid":301354,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 推介比各位日常番同好] GA 芸術科アートデザインクラス","createTime":"2017-06-28T14:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T17:45:19.000Z","uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57699a64ae4b60c1df3a9f4375cdff149bcbcbf8","tid":301354,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"(坦白講我唔知呢套算唔算出名，實際上TVB有播過)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/oevarfyj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Foevarfyj&h=9aff0dda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n呢套動同漫係講及幾名少女係美術學校嘅點與滴<br />\n<br />\n故事內容我唔多講啦，比大家去發掘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過其中不得不提嘅係佢地嘅CV陣容<br />\n左下角果位就係主角，由戶松遙配音，果然聽果時完全唔知佢係邊個嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次就係中間果位角色，由澤城姐姐配音<br />\n澤城將佢配到好男人之外，仲一人配兩角，配到佢阿哥成個女人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他唔多講，不過就故事而言一定啱哂各位日常番同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bc05bf71244ee1ae9eaca0f48a3e6c6d7822e4","tid":301354,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:45:54.000Z","msg":"扮咩正經"},{"pid":"8d6d2a83974190ba6e2ce7cfe0a092bcef022619","tid":301354,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:47:36.000Z","msg":"樓豬低汁會然"},{"pid":"cd737aae9ef20af4987d95317a098d86481245f5","tid":301354,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"TVB配得幾好笑<br />\n又輕鬆<br />\n<br />\n可惜冷門到日文seed反而仲難搵"},{"pid":"789a86ff5ee65723559cd0bd1f8b30d87216b88d","tid":301354,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"開個po都比小圈子搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947953b761e21dcab6c7e4f06ac1e4e9324d4ba6","t